    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;In order to meet the evolving needs of the Internet community, the canonical format for RFCs is changing from a plain-text, ASCII-only format to an XML format that will, in turn, be rendered into several publication formats.  This document defines the HTML format that will be rendered for an RFC or Internet-Draft.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
